nkurencyjne, nie wahaj si\u0119 ich zmienia\u0107.<\/li>\n<li><b>Wykorzystuj promocje:<\/b> Okazjonalne promocje czy obni\u017cki cen mog\u0105 przyci\u0105gn\u0105\u0107 nowych klient\u00f3w. Zastan\u00f3w si\u0119 nad strategi\u0105 cenow\u0105, kt\u00f3ra uwzgl\u0119dnia sezonowe wyprzeda\u017ce lub oferty specjalne.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Podsumowuj\u0105c, skuteczne zarz\u0105dzanie cenami na Amazonie wymaga ci\u0105g\u0142ej analizy i elastyczno\u015bci. Pami\u0119taj, aby regularnie monitorowa\u0107 rynek i dostosowywa\u0107 swoje strategie cenowe. <b>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<h2>Jak skutecznie zarz\u0105dza\u0107 cenami na Amazonie?<\/h2>\n<p>Dlaczego tak wielu sprzedawc\u00f3w na Amazonie<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":4277,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[2],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4276","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-kontent"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4276"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4276"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4276\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4277"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4276"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4276"},{"tax